title.rendered: iSense Extra Nitrile Premium Medical Exam Disposable Gloves – Large

content.rendered:
iSense extra white medical safe nitrile disposable gloves provide protection against bacteria, viruses and infection.

Areas of use:

  • Medical personnel
  • Laboratory technicians
  • Housekeepers
  • Automotive workers
  • Food handlers
  • Gardeners
  • Product inspectors
  • Furniture refinishers

excerpt.rendered: TGA Registered Class 1 Medical Device290mm extended length for extra protectionWhite Nitrile with textured fingertipsHigh Puncture ResistanceSuperior Chemical ResistanceLatex free, vinyl free, powder free, MBT freeARTG No-  333734
